    "120424501": {
      "title": "2-to-1 maps with hereditarily indecomposable images",
      "abstract": "It is shown that there is no 2-to-I map from the pseudoarc, or any treelike continuum, onto a hereditarily indecomposable continuum, and that no hereditarily indecomposable treelike continuum can be the image of a 2-to-I map."
